//lih.kg/1078964\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1078964</a><br />\n<br />\n(多圖整合) 香港騙案？整霓虹燈個位巴打上次kickstarter都走咗數<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1102694\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1102694</a><br />\n<br />\n[人血饅頭] kickstarter霓虹燈撚又出嚟呃錢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1556249\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1556249</a><br />\n<br />\n[DGX團隊] 懷疑HK Apocalypse未經授權拎願榮光去賣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675418\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675418</a><br />\n<br />\n（人血饅頭食到笑）咪再幫襯HK Apocalypse<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1679008\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1679008</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（乜又係你呀）原來和你宵個搞手就係HK Apocalypse 班底<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1766828\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1766828</a>"},{"pid":"65e4832fecc51e206872128362a529e31ef5d676","tid":1773154,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T10:02:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e48c2d2e61432239ff58ea5dff91cd1f55bb0e44","tid":1773154,"uid":231933,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T10:04:50.000Z","msg":"相信越來越多人用手足和黃色經濟圈的名義 cap 水，大家要小心。"},{"pid":"519f63769cb57a758e46363245b443e0adf6dd23","tid":1773154,"uid":71253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T10:05:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />bob叔筆錢點算"},{"pid":"b568dfea2dfe8cd685c97c0268b1fd62ce9d4188","tid":1773154,"uid":314319,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T10:13:46.000Z","msg":"去返黃店食算啦，行少次年宵又唔會死<br />\n而依條仆街就一定要清算，搞大佢、幫佢出名<br />\n香港人唔係好恰架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd