/1675418/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1675418/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 扮搵區議員做監察人 區議員張浚偉：我不是監察人<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/7mjBGLG.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 被爆出梁樂聞Lokson有誠信問題後，話會退出團隊。4/12凌晨梁樂聞Lokson(Steve)已經用自己方式重新奪得眾籌款項的絕對控制權。另外再踢走團隊其他成員，務求自己分到最大果塊餅<br />\n<br />\n4.打手足<br />\n物資站無得到主辦認可籌款+打手足+影大頭 事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/c/1225551555/35912\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fc%2F1225551555%2F35912&d=dMuVdPjJf30Qxtl2jkPsRPzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=b3b73ebf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/c/1225551555/35912</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/HKStationary/173\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKStationary%2F173&d=dMuVdPjJf30Qxtl2jkPsRPzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=cb7bf67f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKStationary/173</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T10:19:11.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講多d第4點？呢單冇聽過<br />\n同埋第一條link 唔喺嗰個group入唔到，有冇 cap 圖？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BBOjsVx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBBOjsVx.png&h=c62ac105&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f4dc0416853fb0158eda6ba251d9f78e1b6965e8","tid":1773154,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T10:20:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05a6df19cb438e6fed7dfa5317e62eed40150f85","tid":1773154,"uid":171583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T10:20:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5390f6ec42cdb0c6f0fc6821301a280ebea064dd","tid":1773154,"uid":171583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T10:20:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8473faa5366b6e78bc60bb88438e42f8ac8668cb","ti